---
// WhyItMatters Section - Benefits of spec-driven development
---

<section class="section why-it-matters" id="why-it-matters">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="why-grid">
			<div class="why-content">
				<h2>Why Spec-Driven Development Matters</h2>
				<p class="lead-text">
					In the age of AI-assisted coding, the bottleneck isn't writing code‚Äîit's knowing <em>what</em> to build and <em>why</em>.
				</p>

				<div class="key-benefits">
					<div class="key-benefit">
						<div class="benefit-icon">üéØ</div>
						<div>
							<h3>Crystal-Clear Direction</h3>
							<p>No mid-project pivots or wasted sprints. Everyone knows what success looks like.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="key-benefit">
						<div class="benefit-icon">‚ö°</div>
						<div>
							<h3>Faster AI Collaboration</h3>
							<p>Transform vague prompts into precise implementations with structured specs.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="key-benefit">
						<div class="benefit-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
						<div>
							<h3>Reduced Technical Debt</h3>
							<p>Architectural decisions made upfront, not hastily patched later.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="why-visual">
				<div class="stats-card">
					<div class="stat">
						<div class="stat-number">10x</div>
						<div class="stat-label">Faster Planning</div>
						<div class="stat-desc">With AI-assisted spec generation</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat">
						<div class="stat-number">85%</div>
						<div class="stat-label">Fewer Rewrites</div>
						<div class="stat-desc">Clear requirements from the start</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat">
						<div class="stat-number">100%</div>
						<div class="stat-label">Team Alignment</div>
						<div class="stat-desc">Single source of truth for all</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.why-it-matters {
		background: var(--color-pastel-yellow);
	}

	.why-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
		gap: var(--space-16);
		align-items: center;
	}

	.why-content h2 {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
	}

	.lead-text {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
	}

	.key-benefits {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-6);
	}

	.key-benefit {
		display: flex;
		gap: var(--space-4);
		align-items: flex-start;
	}

	.benefit-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.key-benefit h3 {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
	}

	.key-benefit p {
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	/* Stats Visual */
	.stats-card {
		background: var(--color-white);
		padding: var(--space-10);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal-lg);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-8);
	}

	.stat {
		text-align: center;
		padding: var(--space-6);
		background: var(--color-pastel-pink);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal-sm);
	}

	.stat-number {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		font-weight: 900;
		line-height: 1;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.stat-label {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
	}

	.stat-desc {
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	@media (max-width: 968px) {
		.why-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: var(--space-12);
		}
	}
</style>
